I"4<p>A day-long session ( <strong>5.5 hours</strong> ) on Introduction to Deep Learning in Jadavpur University Information Technology department was conducted.</p>

<p>Concepts explained were Perceptron , Activation Functions , Forward Propagation , Backward propagation , Gradient Descent , Stochastic Gradient Descent , Mini Batch Gradient Descent , Dropout , Transfer Learning and also CNN Concepts such as Filters , Pooling .</p>

<p>The theory was interspersed with generous coding demos. The attendees also did an extensive hands-on for more than 2 hours.</p>
